msgstr "Minecraft 1.16 及後續版本"

msgid ""
"On recent versions of Minecraft, you can use %s on an unmodified Vanilla "
"server. To do so, add the following arguments before you specify the jar "
"file when you start the server:"
msgstr ""
"在較新版本的 Minecraft 上，您可以在原版伺服器上使用 %s 。只需在啟動伺服器時，"
"在指定 jar 檔案之前新增以下參數："

msgid "For example, the full command you use to start the server might be:"
msgstr "例如，啟動伺服器的完整指令可能是："

msgid "In <code>server.properties</code>, set <code>enforce-secure-profile=false</code>."
msgstr ""
"在 <code>server.properties</code> 中，設定 <code>enforce-secure-"
"profile=false</code>。"

